               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡, Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>


                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from = "1r" to = "24v"/>
                    <title type = "complete" ref="LIT4112Salam"/>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                      ሰላም፡ ስላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ ሐዋዝ። እምነ፡ ከልበሌ፡ ወቈስጥ፡ ወእምነ፡ ሰንበልት፡ ምዑዝ።
                    </incipit>
                    <note>Incomplete because of erasure to make room for the miniatures. Chaîne, Répertoire, no. 220; MG 59, pp. 735ff</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from = "25r" to = "46r"/>
                    <title type = "complete" ref="LIT4131Salam"/>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                      ...በቋሉ፤ ወጽፉቅ፡ ጥቀ፡ ለአርዘ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ ቈጽሉ። ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ካህናትል ዘላዕለ፡ ኵሉ።
                    </incipit>
                    <note><locus target = "#24v #36r"/> erased to make room for the picture. Chaîne, Répertoire, no. 123; EMIP, 26, f. 47r</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from = "46r" to = "59v"/>
                    <title type = "complete" ref="LIT4112Salam"/>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                      ለዘኢየፈቅረኪ፡ እግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ውኩፈ፡ ኢይኩን፡ ጸሎቱ፡...
                    </incipit>
                    <note>Missed text from the Image of Mary, <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ዘተረስዓ፡ ናይ፡ መልአ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign> The note is in Gə'əz and Təgrəñña</note>
                  </msItem>

